Wolfblade:
 
The femme slowly sat up, and turned on the bed to face Windlord.
"Look around this room.  It is filled with Malice's things.  Each object means something, it's all a part of him.  I want him back, I love him.  Don't sully his name because of something they forced him to do.  I'm sorry I yelled at you, but don't ever talk about Malice like that again."

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
Windlord:

"I just liked to say, I sorry"said Windlord while he closed his eyes 
and low his head"If hit me and insult me, makes you feel better... 
go ahead"
